{"tid":600143,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"讀緊大學有感而發","createTime":"2018-03-21T05:10:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T15:48:54.000Z","uid":31173,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"15a6399876d29f4ca5233e00873deee8cfff74b4","tid":600143,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T05:10:41.000Z","msg":"讀左幾年，發覺每次溫書其實都係為左考試，雖然讀個陣係有興趣想知點解，想了解下，但其實考完試就會唔記得晒，咁到底其實有冇意義？ 你問番我呢幾年學左D咩，我其實唔太講得出，<br />\n<br />\n有次睇番上個sem其中一份notes，我望完完全唔記得晒，睇番其實由0開始，最多係有少少印象，咁其實我個陣捱更抵夜溫書嘅時間有冇充實咁善用到？"},{"pid":"a220db41f1d04d7f71dbb3263857916c3f73aec8","tid":600143,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T05:18:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee7dc7f16f75e13239dbf0593b9cbb012b1f459","tid":600143,"uid":146299,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T05:19:18.000Z","msg":"好現實啦 為左個degree"},{"pid":"d19a63b1783679e120836db06deb72e0d704e13a","tid":600143,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ee7dc7f16f75e13239dbf0593b9cbb012b1f459","tid":600143,"uid":146299,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T05:19:18.000Z","msg":"好現實啦 為左個degree"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T06:03:37.000Z","msg":"想問讀左幾年次次考完試都唔記得晒其實讀書黎有冇意義？"},{"pid":"71e3f16f3f0ce957030f04cfcbe14d4d8e32f3e9","tid":600143,"uid":86403,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T06:17:03.000Z","msg":"真係好現實<br />\n咁耐都係學點樣考試拎分,唔係學拎個個範疇既知識架啦"},{"pid":"9531dd4a82abc9d1386c0e3319dcd74bf3c2b2f2","tid":600143,"uid":156948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T06:20:19.000Z","msg":"唔可以咁講 如果你只係每次考之前先溫書 溫到嘅內容好快會唔記得 但係如果你係每日都keep住溫就唔會咁"},{"pid":"62ac8cd1345eac4d51ed60ba25d96ba720f897b4","tid":600143,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d19a63b1783679e120836db06deb72e0d704e13a","tid":600143,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ee7dc7f16f75e13239dbf0593b9cbb012b1f459","tid":600143,"uid":146299,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T05:19:18.000Z","msg":"好現實啦 為左個degree"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T06:03:37.000Z","msg":"想問讀左幾年次次考完試都唔記得晒其實讀書黎有冇意義？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T06:21:33.000Z","msg":"主要因為學d嘢你唔感興趣，唔喺自發去學，所以你間硬溫完之後你唔記得"},{"pid":"c9a99b21ab5f457a52499054b441452f0108ee40","tid":600143,"uid":21699,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T06:54:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b771dfb1f268ca7ac9122b21cbeb4ee4278b91a5","tid":600143,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T15:32:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4c8ceb2890b81ba8a4228a2c13d7f2f088eb21","tid":600143,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-21T15:48:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\nExam based係咁。因為個curriculum擺係到，限制左你淨係溫slide上面既野。你一自己溫其他野，你就可能考得冇其他人咁好，咁樣係discourage緊人去探索新知識<br />\n<br />\n建議平日都睇下d materials，而唔係考試前先臨急臨忙睇，冇時間壓迫，你就會有興趣去學。自己搵黎學既野係記憶較深，因為你會將成個argument run 一次/自己extract個knowledge出黎<br />\n<br />\n所以我一向唔同意大學既科係exam based<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以assessment 用 assignment, project, workshop甚至係industrial 甚至係industrial placement 都好過exam"}]}